description.p:
As a fourth aspect of the embodiment, an apparatus for mobility management is provided. The apparatus is configured to

send cell set information of a cell set to a source cell set;

receive information about selection of the cell set, which is sent by the source cell set according to the cell set information; and

decide information about at least one target cell in the cell set according to the information about selection of the cell set, and sending the information about the at least one target cell to the source cell set so that the source cell set provides the information about the at least one target cell to a user equipment for handover;

wherein the apparatus comprises:

a target cell deciding unit, configured to decide the information about the at least one target cell in the cell set according to identifiers of all or part of the cells in the cell set and resource occupancy of the cell set when the information about selection comprises the identifiers of all or part of the cells in the cell set and an identifier of the cell set.

In the method, the sending control information to the user equipment through a control channel of the source cell and/or the target cell after sending the resource reallocation message comprises:

sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell and keeping sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message; and stopping sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell when a resource reallocation completion message from the user equipment is received;

or,
sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell and stopping sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message;

or,
keeping sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message; and stopping sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell and sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell when a resource reallocation completion message from the user equipment is received.

In the apparatus, the handover control unit is configured to:

send control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell and keep sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message; and stop sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell when a resource reallocation completion message from the user equipment is received;

or,
send control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell and stop sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message;

or,
the handover control unit is configured to keep sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell after sending the resource reallocation message; and stop sending control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the source cell and send control information to the user equipment through the control channel of the target cell when a resource reallocation completion message from the user equipment is received.

In an example of the present invention, a user equipment is provided, the user equipment comprises:

a resource reallocation message receiving unit, configured to receive a resource reallocation message that carries information about a target cell from a source cell;
a handover executing unit, configured to stop receiving control information from a control channel of the source cell and receive control information from a control channel of the target cell after receiving the resource reallocation message from the source cell;

and
a resource reallocation completion message sending unit, configured to send a resource reallocation completion message to the target cell after resource reallocation is completed.

claim.claim-text:
A method for mobility management, comprising:
obtaining (S301), by a source cell set, cell set information sent by a cell set in an access network, wherein the cell set includes at least two cells which are capable of simultaneously communicating with a user equipment;
by the source cell set, selecting (S303), for a user equipment, a target cell set to which the user equipment may hand over according to the cell set information, and sending information about selection of the target cell set to the target cell set, wherein the information sent by the source cell set to the target cell set comprises identifiers of all or part of cells in the target cell set.

An apparatus for mobility management, comprising:
a cell set information obtaining unit (401), configured to obtain cell set information sent by a cell set in an access network, wherein the cell set includes at least two cells which are capable of simultaneously communicating with a user equipment;
a target cell set selecting unit (403), configured to select, for a user equipment, a target cell set to which the user equipment may hand over according to the cell set information, and send information about selection of the target cell set to the target cell set, wherein the information sent by the source cell set to the target cell set comprises identifiers of all or part of cells in the target cell set.
